<body>
<button id="theme-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Toggle light and dark theme" title="Toggle light/dark">🌙</button><button id="print-btn" type="button" aria-label="Print" title="Print">🖨️</button>
<article class="dg">
<div class="dg-topbar"> <a class="dig" data-type="summary" data-t="65">↑ summary</a> <button class="dg-expand-all">⤢ expand all</button> <a class="ask-ai" data-ai-prompt="Please review this video first; I'd like to ask questions about it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vid9" data-ai-url="https://gemini.google.com/app?prompt=Please%20review%20this%20video%20first%3B%20I'd%20like%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20it%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvid9&amp;autosubmit=false">💬 Ask AI about this video</a> <span class="dg-size" role="group" aria-label="Slide image size"><button class="dg-size-dec" type="button" aria-label="Smaller slides">−</button><input class="dg-size-range" type="range" min="50" max="150" step="10" value="100" aria-label="Slide image size percent"><button class="dg-size-inc" type="button" aria-label="Larger slides">+</button><button class="dg-size-val" type="button" aria-label="Reset slide image size to 100%">100%</button></span> <button class="dg-caps-toggle" type="button" aria-pressed="true" aria-label="Toggle slide captions">▣ captions</button></div>
<section data-start="65" data-dug="true">
<h2>1. A <a class="ts" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vid9&amp;t=65s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">▶ (1:05)</a> <a class="dig-toggle">show summary ⌃</a> <a class="dig-refresh" data-section="65">↻ outdated</a> <a class="ask-ai" data-ai-prompt="Please review this section of the video (from 1:05 to 2:00), then I'd like to ask questions about it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vid9&amp;t=65s" data-ai-url="https://gemini.google.com/app?prompt=Please%20review%20this%20section%20of%20the%20video%20(from%201%3A05%20to%202%3A00)%2C%20then%20I'd%20like%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20it%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvid9%26t%3D65s&amp;autosubmit=false">💬 ask AI</a></h2><div class="dug"><p>body</p>
</div>
</section>
<section data-start="120" data-dug="false">
<h2>2. B <a class="ts" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vid9&amp;t=120s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">▶ (2:00)</a> <a class="dig-trigger" data-section="120">dig deeper ▶</a> <a class="ask-ai" data-ai-prompt="Please review this section of the video (from 2:00 onward), then I'd like to ask questions about it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vid9&amp;t=120s" data-ai-url="https://gemini.google.com/app?prompt=Please%20review%20this%20section%20of%20the%20video%20(from%202%3A00%20onward)%2C%20then%20I'd%20like%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20it%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvid9%26t%3D120s&amp;autosubmit=false">💬 ask AI</a></h2>
</section>
</article>

<div id="_dg-ea-dlg" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="_dg-ea-msg">
  <div class="_dg-box">
    <p id="_dg-ea-msg"></p>
    <button id="_dg-ea-confirm">Confirm</button>
    <button id="_dg-ea-cancel-dlg">Cancel</button>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="_dg-ea-prog" role="region" aria-label="Expand-all progress">
  <div class="_dg-bar">
    <span id="_dg-ea-prog-msg" role="status" aria-live="polite">Starting…</span>
    <span id="_dg-ea-fail-msg" aria-live="polite" style="color:#c00;display:none"></span>
    <button id="_dg-ea-cancel-prog">Cancel</button>
  </div>
</div>
